<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="w-full px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 xl:px-20 2xl:px-28">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 opacity-0-initial" data-animate="section-title">
        Tentang Saya
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-soft-blue mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 space-y-4 opacity-0-initial" data-animate="card">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-soft-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-soft-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Latar Belakang</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Lulusan Teknik Informatika dari Politeknik Negeri Malang dengan IPK 3.73/4.00. Memiliki kemampuan dalam pengolahan data, pengelolaan administrasi dokumen, serta pengembangan website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 space-y-4 opacity-0-initial" data-animate="card">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-soft-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-soft-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Pengalaman</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Berpengalaman dalam mendukung operasional proyek, menganalisis kebutuhan sistem, serta membantu perancangan solusi yang efektif dan terstruktur.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 space-y-4 opacity-0-initial" data-animate="card">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-soft-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-soft-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Kelebihan</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Detail, komunikatif dalam tim, motivasi tinggi, dan kemampuan adaptasi yang baik terhadap perubahan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 space-y-4 opacity-0-initial" data-animate="card">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-soft-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-soft-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/>
            <path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Pendidikan</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          D4 Teknik Informatika (IPK 3.73) dan D3 Manajemen Informatika (IPK 3.75) di Politeknik Negeri Malang.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
